abstract: The Commercial Aircraft Corporation of China won its first overseas regional-jet order, worth about $750 million, from General Electric.
snippet: The Commercial Aircraft Corporation of China won its first overseas regional-jet order, worth about $750 million, from General Electric.
lead_paragraph: The Commercial Aircraft Corporation of China won its first overseas regional-jet order, worth about $750 million, from General Electric as China aims to challenge the dominance of Boeing and Airbus in the aviation market.

headline.main: G.E. Orders Jets Made by China
headline.print_headline: G.E. Orders Jets Made in China

abstract: In the latest setback for the new plane, the Boeing 787 will not make its first test flight this year because of delays caused by a strike of the machinists union, the airplane maker said.
snippet: In the latest setback for the new plane, the Boeing 787 will not make its first test flight this year because of delays caused by a strike of the machinists union, the airplane maker said.
lead_paragraph: The Boeing Company said Tuesday that its new long-range airplane, the 787, would not make its first test flight this year because of delays caused by a machinists’ strike.

headline.main: Boeing Postpones Test Flight of the 787
headline.print_headline: Boeing Postpones Test Flight Of the 787
